               <p>191. 
               
                  <persName id="t17400416-1-defend28" type="defendantName">
                     Mary 
                     Wharton 
                  <interp inst="t17400416-1-defend28" type="surname" value="Wharton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-defend28" type="given" value="Mary"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-defend28" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             , of <placeName id="t17400416-1-defloc1">Christ-Church, London</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17400416-1-defloc1" type="placeName" value="Christ-Church, London"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17400416-1-defloc1" type="type" value="defendantHome"></interp>
                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400416-1-defend28 t17400416-1-defloc1"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17400416-1-off2" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-off2" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-off2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a Pewter Gallon-pot, val. 4 s.
            </rs> the Goods of 
               <persName id="t17400416-1-victim29" type="victimName">
                  Benj
                   . Marriot
               <interp inst="t17400416-1-victim29" type="surname" value=". Marriot"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-victim29" type="given" value="Benj"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-victim29" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400416-1-off2 t17400416-1-victim29"></join>
                  </persName>
            , <rs id="t17400416-1-cd3" type="crimeDate">March 13</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400416-1-off2 t17400416-1-cd3"></join>.</p>
               <p>Mr. Marriot. On the 13th of March last, the Prisoner came to my Shop, and asked the Price of Salt. - I <rs id="t17400416-1-viclabel4" type="occupation">keep an Oil-shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400416-1-victim29 t17400416-1-viclabel4"></join> in <placeName id="t17400416-1-crimeloc5">Newgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17400416-1-crimeloc5" type="placeName" value="Newgate-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17400416-1-crimeloc5" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400416-1-off2 t17400416-1-crimeloc5"></join>. She told me her Mistress wanted some Salt, and had ordered her to wait in my Shop till she came; and therefore, with my Leave, she would sit down: and accordingly she sat her self down by a Vinegar-Cask; near which the Pewter Gallon-pot stood. After she had set a while in the Shop, she got up, and bid me weigh the Salt, while she stepp'd thro' Newgate for 2 Gallons of Gin, and then she would come again. As soon as she was gone, I miss'd the Gallon-Pot; upon which I went after her, and took her in Phoenix-Court , with the Pot upon her. She told me, her Necessity made her do it, and begg'd that I would not send her to Newgate, but rather let her go to Bridewell. <rs id="t17400416-1-verdict6" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-verdict6" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-verdict6" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17400416-1-punish7" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-punish7" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17400416-1-punish7" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="whipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17400416-1-defend28 t17400416-1-punish7"></join>
               
                     <note>[Whipping. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
